title: I got Riot Kayle but not my summoner's icon
body: Am I still going to get my icon I was looking forward to it :(

replies.body: The gifts are still being sent out, and they're not all going to arrived at the same time.  Details and our current timeline are provided through our current [support banner](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/227317608--Sept-14-Anniversary-gifts-are-currently-being-distributed-You-may-not-receive-them-right-away-so-please-be-patient-).  The goods will come!
